OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, sunny
OL,6,Fand warm evening for most, but perhaps
OL,7,Fmore in the way of cloud across
OL,8,Fnorthern Perthshire. Dry for the rest
OL,9,Fof the night with clear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FDry with a good deal of warm
OL,12,Fsunshine. However more in the way of
OL,13,Fcloud around eastern coasts where it
OL,14,Fwill feel cooler than Monday.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry and bright with a good deal of
OL,18,Fsunshine. Warm inland, but cooler
OL,19,Falong the east coast on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
